com.Cardinal.CommandPackage.Entity

Class ListEmbed

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.Cardinal.CommandPackage.Entity.ListEmbed

  • public class ListEmbed
extends java.lang.Object
    I class used to create embed objects in an ordered list/paged fashion. If ever you wish to customize the look of the embed, the builder can be obtained via getBuilder().
    Author:
    Cardinal System
